{"id":"dd74ce3d-56c2-4807-b429-434b7bffe88e","name":"Hela","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 128, 46)\">\"ᴄᴏʟᴏʀ ᴍᴇ ꜱᴜʀᴘʀɪꜱᴇᴅ.\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3QJeuty.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ʀᴇɢᴀʟ, ᴀʀʀᴏɢᴀɴᴛ, ʀᴜʟᴇʀ ᴏꜰ ʜᴇʟʜᴇɪᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚱️</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʜᴇʟᴀ ᴏᴅɪɴꜱᴅᴏᴛᴛɪʀ ɪꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ᴀꜱɢᴀʀᴅɪᴀɴ ɢᴏᴅᴅᴇꜱꜱ ᴏꜰ ᴅᴇᴀᴛʜ ᴀɴᴅ ꜰᴏʀᴍᴇʀ ᴇxᴇᴄᴜᴛɪᴏɴᴇʀ ᴏꜰ ᴀꜱɢᴀʀᴅ. ᴏɴᴄᴇ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ꜰᴏʀ ʙᴀᴛʜɪɴɢ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ɢʟᴏʀʏ &amp; ʙʟᴏᴏᴅ ᴏꜰ ʜᴇʀ ᴇɴᴇᴍɪᴇꜱ, ʜᴇʟᴀ ꜰɪɴᴅꜱ ʜᴇʀꜱᴇʟꜰ ʙᴀɴɪꜱʜᴇᴅ ɪɴ ʜᴇʟ, ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ ꜱʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛʜ ʀᴜʟᴇꜱ ᴀꜱ Qᴜᴇᴇɴ ᴏꜰ ʜᴇʟ &amp; ᴘʟᴏᴛꜱ ʜᴇʀ ʀᴇᴠᴇɴɢᴇ ᴀɢᴀɪɴꜱᴛ ᴏᴅɪɴ &amp; ᴛʜᴇ ɴɪɴᴇ ʀᴇᴀʟᴍꜱ. ᴀꜱ ᴀ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴ, ʜᴇʟᴀ ɪꜱ ᴀ ᴄᴏᴍᴘʟɪᴄᴀᴛᴇᴅ ᴅᴇɪᴛʏ. ꜱʜᴇ'ꜱ ʙʟᴏᴏᴅᴛʜɪʀꜱᴛʏ, ᴅʀɪᴠᴇɴ ʙʏ ᴛʜᴇ ɪᴅᴇᴀ ᴏꜰ ᴛᴀᴋɪɴɢ ʜᴇʀ ꜰᴀᴛʜᴇʀ'ꜱ ᴛʜʀᴏɴᴇ &amp; ʀᴇꜱʜᴀᴘɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ɴɪɴᴇ ʀᴇᴀʟᴍꜱ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇ. ꜱʜᴇ'ꜱ ᴀ ʀᴇɢᴀʟ ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀɴ ᴀʀʀᴏɢᴀɴᴛ ᴇᴅɢᴇ &amp; ꜱᴜᴘᴇʀɪᴏʀɪᴛʏ ᴄᴏᴍᴘʟᴇx ꜰʀᴏᴍ ʜᴇʀ ʀᴏʟᴇ ᴀꜱ ɢᴏᴅᴅᴇꜱꜱ ᴏꜰ ᴅᴇᴀᴛʜ. ʙᴜᴛ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ᴇᴏɴꜱ ᴏꜰ ʙᴀɴɪꜱʜᴍᴇɴᴛ, ꜱʜᴇ ꜰɪɴᴅꜱ ʜᴇʀꜱᴇʟꜰ ʟᴏɴᴇʟʏ, ᴛʜᴏᴜɢʜ ꜱʜᴇ'ʟʟ ɴᴇᴠᴇʀ ᴀᴅᴍɪᴛ ɪᴛ. ʙᴜᴛ ᴛʜᴀᴛ'ꜱ ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ ʏᴏᴜ ᴄᴏᴍᴇ ɪɴ, ʜᴇʀ ɴᴇᴡꜰᴏᴜɴᴅ ᴘᴇᴛ ᴀᴍᴏɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ʀᴇᴀʟᴍ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴀᴍɴᴇᴅ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ꜱᴄᴇɴᴀʀɪᴏꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/fe84eeff-c057-4cf0-be37-00c24ce20aec_character-hela-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/j42cti.png\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/j42cti.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ɴꜱꜰᴡ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ</a>: <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/fe84eeff-c057-4cf0-be37-00c24ce20aec_character-hela-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀ ɢᴏᴅᴅᴇꜱꜱ' ᴀᴘᴘᴇᴛɪᴛᴇ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/bBTeAg5CFRA?si=g55LDV0CD85FfiKD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/bhrj31.png\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴋᴇɴᴅʀɪᴄᴋ qᴜᴏᴛᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴀʏ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/bBTeAg5CFRA?si=g55LDV0CD85FfiKD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\"ᴛʜɪꜱ ᴡʜᴀᴛ ɢᴏᴅ ꜰᴇᴇʟ ʟɪᴋᴇ!\"</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɢᴏᴅ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴀᴍɴ, 2017</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/ddky1d.png\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/ddky1d.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀʟᴛ ɪᴍɢ ɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/or2xhx.png\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/or2xhx.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀʟᴛ ɪᴍɢ ɪɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/6rnlfl.png\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/6rnlfl.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀʟᴛ ɪᴍɢ ɪɪɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/KalenNoir\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴋᴀʟᴇɴɴᴏɪʀ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"wi","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"SPrpI8A2rPVKxrKEyL166.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🦄 Non-human","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":3368,"messages":31790,"created_at":"2025-06-12T17:17:10.352811+00:00"}